name: Spirax S5 CFD M 50
description: Premium Performance Off-Highway Caterpillar Final Drive and Axle Oil

localDocs.name: Spirax S5 CFD M 50 United States EN TDG V2.2 24-Jun-2016
Spirax S5 CFD M 50 United States EN 140002686046 EHS V4.3 10-JUL-2020

marketing: Shell Spirax S5 CFD M 50 is a dedicated final drive and axle oil which offers significantly improved protection for gears and bearings in bevel gears, differentials, final drives and axles. It meets the Caterpillar FD-1 final drive axle oil (FDAO) specification. Spirax S5 CFD M 50 has been developed for continuous use in extreme ambient temperatures in off-road vehicles.
